# Regenerate: vhs docs/guide/niftycli-new/demo-new.tape (run from repo root)
Output public/assets/images/demo-new.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 60ms

Hide
Type "source docs/guide/niftycli-new/demo-new-setup.sh"
Enter
Show

Type "niftycli new"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "Fix login bug"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "Login fails for SSO users on Safari"
Enter
Sleep 3s
